Detailed Description

cvmx_ciu_en2_pp::_ip3_w1c

Notes: Write-1-to-clear version of the CIU_EN2_PP(IO)X_IPx(INT) register, read back corresponding CIU_EN2_PP(IO)X_IPx(INT) value.
